entry.def: A sub-editor is a person whose job it is to check and correct articles in newspapers or magazines before they are printed.

example.ex: I was a sub-editor on the foreign desk of the News Chronicle.
example.tran: 我是《新闻纪事报》国际组的一名助理编辑。
